PipelineDisplayName: The name of the pipeline that will be display in the import dialog.
ReimportPropertyStrategy: Set the reimport strategy when reimporting into the level.
bDeleteMissingActors: If enabled, deletes actors that were not part of the translation when reimporting into a level.
bForceReimportDeletedActors: If enabled, respawns actors that were deleted in the editor prior to a reimport.
bForceReimportDeletedAssets: If enabled, recreates assets that were deleted in the editor prior to reimporting into a level.
bDeleteMissingAssets: If enabled, deletes assets that were not part of the translation when reimporting into a level.
bUsePhysicalInsteadOfStandardPerspective: Disable this option to not convert Standard(Perspective) to Physical Cameras
